data.description: Welcome to the timberlakes community! This is a wonderful 3 Bedroom 2 bath home with a double lot in the quiet community of timberlakes. Located just 20 minutes from shelton you will gain access to parks, beaches, a multifunctional sports court, and fresh/saltwater boat launches. There is Plenty of storage space in the detached garage for a woodshop, boats, or cars! This home has a very spacious and open yard. New Anderson windows were installed with a warranty that is transferable to the new owner! The home also boasts a wood stove to keep you more than warm in the winter months and new LVP flooring that makes cleaning a breeze! The home also comes with a RV hook up and enough space to park a 5th wheel.
